snippet.title: Hard Work Trailer (All Ages)
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Matchasoft's upcoming erotic visual novel, Hard Work. The game is being published by Denpasoft, and a demo can be found on both the Denpasoft and Matchasoft websites.

Composition: Mondonater
Vocals: 榊原ゆい
Lyrics: 桑原聖
Arrangement: 矢鴇つかさ
